--- parseTerminalWatchArgs() ---
  ✅ extracts session id from direct command
  ✅ parses --size width
  ✅ parses --size height
  ✅ parses --interval-ms
  ✅ parses --max-chars inline form
  ✅ accepts valid options without errors
  ✅ reports invalid size, height, and unknown option
  ✅ extracts session id from /watch alias
  ✅ accepts /watch alias without treating it as an argument

--- tailTextForTerminal() ---
  ✅ keeps last height lines and trims long lines from the left
  ✅ renders empty logs explicitly

--- formatTerminalWatchMessage() ---
  ✅ formats live watch title
  ✅ includes session id
  ✅ sanitizes nested code fences in logs
