  ✅ polls the session more than once while the watch is active
  ✅ does not edit Telegram message when terminal snapshot is unchanged
  ✅ edits Telegram exactly once for one changed terminal snapshot
  ✅ counts only changed terminal snapshots as updates

--- /terminal_watch requester access and /watch alias (Issue #1778) ---
